        # pickleDB
        pickleDB is lightweight, fast, and simple database based on the
        [json](https://docs.python.org/3/library/json.html) module.
        And it's BSD licensed!
        
        
        ## pickleDB is Fun
        ```python
        >>> import pickledb
        
        >>> db = pickledb.load('test.db', False)
        
        >>> db.set('key', 'value')
        
        >>> db.get('key')
        'value'
        
        >>> db.dump()
        True
        ```
        
        ## Easy to Install
        ```python
        $ pip install pickledb
        ```
        
